<chapter id="Chapter528660">
  <title>Work Order (W/O) Module</title>

  <para id="Para524650">In this chapter, we describe the Manufacturing module.
  This is the module where Work Orders are created, maintained, and executed.
  A <anchor id="Anchor532397" role="Index"
  xreflabel="work orders:five states of" /> <indexterm significance="normal"
      zone="Anchor532397">
      <primary>work orders</primary>

      <secondary>five states of</secondary>
    </indexterm>Work Order is an authorization to perform manufacturing
  activities. The following topics will be covered:</para>

